there are different installation methods to govern terraform and all of them are listed below as follows;

1. Manually- thsi can be done by either downloading pre-compiled binary (download and move to your required path) or compile by source (by cloning it form Github repo and install it)
2. Mac OS- using package manager home brew is easiest & simpier
3. Win OS- using package manager called chocolatey & install it
4. Linux OS- install some packages & then add HashiCorp repo
        packages varies according to distibution you are choosing to use


to install terraform use: https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/downloads
